  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-70

          -  Schizophrenia, schizoaffective disorder or bipolar disorder

          -  Smoke an average of at least 10 cigarettes per day for at least 1 year

          -  Breath carbon monoxide (CO) levels &gt;8 ppm (if ≤ 8 ppm, then nicotine (NicAlert) Strip
             &gt; 2)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or nursing

          -  Seeking treatment for smoking

          -  Medical contraindications
      </textblock>
